{"tid":2280351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"第一狗官蘇文隆：我依家大撚晒誤指控罪出自《公安條例》 藏索帶少女守行為一年變兩年","createTime":"2020-11-10T12:15:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T13:53:03.000Z","uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"66888c12cd1d697011d21c72de1a186db48a96e8","tid":2280351,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:15:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/DCP5XVZVJFGDVPWTGKNPXVAMKU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FDCP5XVZVJFGDVPWTGKNPXVAMKU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7Iltn4zyk5OLfN8GNswWzUNI%3D&h=22cda209\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201110%2FDCP5XVZVJFGDVPWTGKNPXVAMKU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=5debba2b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201110/DCP5XVZVJFGDVPWTGKNPXVAMKU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n去年11月區區開花，連場反修例抗爭活動中多人被捕被控。有16歲女生在11.11大三罷當日早上，在堵路現場附近管有一包索帶，因而被控管有非法用途工具罪。經商討後，控方今同意撤控，改讓女生守行為一年了事。不過，主任裁判官蘇文隆指控罪涉及《公安條例》，主動提出女生應守行為兩年，更不理辯方更正指控罪實出自《簡易程序治罪條例》，一意孤行命令女生以2,000元簽保守行為兩年。"},{"pid":"c66fb8895a03b99afc66637657c1d4b4a5a08a70","tid":2280351,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:18:20.000Z","msg":"蘇狗：錯又點？我有權力"},{"pid":"e942e3fc02ae23971e91c0e2bc3a40d8428b3acf","tid":2280351,"uid":148315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:36:44.000Z","msg":"一樣適用於黨安法<br />\n<br />\n我話件案都涉及國家安全，唔畀保釋後審<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />審完判返幾碌仲得"},{"pid":"17d02bed6c3c87df923fe1123ad8aed32bf87184","tid":2280351,"uid":282347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"遲啲應該會上訴<br />\n<br />\n不過係律政屍：太輕，要監禁<br />\n<br />\n彭寶琴：冇錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60124801bd78f8f51eb7a9cb5ef7915b2bf9eb2c","tid":2280351,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T12:38:50.000Z","msg":"投訴師召喚<br />\n幾十萬人寄投訴信"},{"pid":"b11a6c0fab029362082f3f3390a3c03392e4b630","tid":2280351,"uid":40520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:50:19.000Z","msg":"大律師公會:我睇唔到<br />\n快d比錢啦"},{"pid":"e9cabefe9e10e9f14eead500b67b7ef669fcb922","tid":2280351,"uid":167928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T13:53:03.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢公安條例定簡易冶罪條例 我蘇文隆就係法律"}]}